cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this repository (compliance engine, LegalRuleML encoding, agiev
  vocabulary, evidence bundles, or study instruments), please cite it using the
  metadata below. If you refer to the research itself, please cite the journal
  article given under preferred-citation. This article supersedes the earlier
  Zenodo preprint (doi:10.5281/zenodo.16284248), which is deprecated and should
  no longer be cited.
title: >-
  AGI Governance Compliance Engine and Evidence Vocabulary (agiev)
